1
00:00:40,280 --> 00:00:41,080
Forgive me, My Lord

2
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:42,840
I did conceal the truth

3
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:45,520
Since I married my husband

4
00:00:46,120 --> 00:00:48,640
I could only bear him two daughters

5
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:50,280
Out of desperation

6
00:00:51,040 --> 00:00:52,120
we bought a woman

7
00:00:53,320 --> 00:00:53,640
Thinking

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:55,280
that if she could give my husband

9
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,640
a little son

10
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,520
and continue the Tian family line, it would be good

11
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,120
The two of us agreed

12
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,680
to tell outsiders that

13
00:01:03,440 --> 00:01:05,640
we found a maid to serve me at home

14
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:09,520
Then why did you fabricate the story of hemorrhage?

15
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:16,440
That was all Tian Wan's sin

16
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,880
Husband, don't be anxious yet

17
00:01:21,440 --> 00:01:23,440
That doctor's diagnosis might not be accurate

18
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,200
If he says it's a girl, it's a girl

19
00:01:29,480 --> 00:01:31,000
Sister, get up first

20
00:01:31,240 --> 00:01:32,080
Don't hurt the baby

21
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:38,360
What use do I have for a daughter?

22
00:01:38,720 --> 00:01:39,680
You broodmare

23
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:42,160
I bought you to give me a son

24
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,360
If you can't bear a son

25
00:01:43,600 --> 00:01:44,880
what do I need you for?

26
00:01:51,080 --> 00:01:52,040
Just strangle her

27
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,240
If this pregnancy is no good

28
00:01:53,520 --> 00:01:54,440
just have another one next time

29
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:57,440
You have the nerve to speak?

30
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,720
If it weren't for your failure

31
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,600
why would I spend money to buy her?

32
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,120
This baby

33
00:02:05,360 --> 00:02:05,760
this baby

34
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,400
I don't want this baby anymore

35
00:02:09,960 --> 00:02:10,400
I don't want it

36
00:02:12,320 --> 00:02:13,560
I don't want this baby anymore

37
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:14,680
I don't want it

38
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:15,560
Bear me another one

39
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:17,320
Bear me another! Bear me another!

40
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,600
That woman was force-fed medicine

41
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:21,320
and miscarried

42
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:24,600
But before that woman could recover

43
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,480
Tian Wan couldn't wait

44
00:02:31,640 --> 00:02:32,040
During the day

45
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,120
Tian Wan locked her in the woodshed

46
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,240
At night

47
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,600
he would carry her into the room

48
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:55,800
Tian Wan was right

49
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,840
In his eyes, that woman was just a broodmare

50
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:01,880
No different

51
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:04,480
from pigs and dogs

52
00:03:47,440 --> 00:03:48,240
As a woman myself,

53
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,120
I couldn't bear to watch any longer.

54
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,520
I was terrified Tian Wan would torture her to death.

55
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:58,120
So I seized the chance to unlock the padlock.

56
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,000
And let her go.

57
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,880
But Tian Wan found out afterwards.

58
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:05,640
He chased her to the outskirts of the city.

59
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:06,760
Stop right there!

60
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,720
Didn't you say you could bear a boy?

61
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:10,240
Give me a boy then!

62
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,360
Give me one!

63
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,080
You broodmare!

64
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,480
Please let her go!

65
00:04:16,720 --> 00:04:17,680
Torturing her like this...

66
00:04:17,960 --> 00:04:18,880
If someone dies...

67
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:21,080
What will we do if the authorities investigate?

68
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:21,640
Get away!

69
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,680
She must be carrying my little son.

70
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,920
Run! Run!

71
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,360
Go on, run!

72
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:29,800
I'll teach you to run!

73
00:04:31,840 --> 00:04:33,760
Is it so hard to give me a child?

74
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,600
I spent so much silver!

75
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:37,080
And didn't hear a single sound!

76
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:46,080
She's dead.

77
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:47,880
Dead.

78
00:04:48,680 --> 00:04:49,200
Dead.

79
00:04:53,120 --> 00:04:53,840
D-Dead.

80
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:55,480
She's dead.

81
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:56,040
Dead.

82
00:04:57,040 --> 00:04:57,440
She's dead.

83
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,240
I didn't mean to do it!

84
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,240
What are you staring at? Hurry up and carry her!

85
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:07,440
Hurry up! Hurry!

86
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:13,160
My Lord.

87
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,920
That is the whole truth.

88
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:18,960
I was afraid that if I got involved in a lawsuit,

89
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:20,680
It would implicate my two daughters.

90
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,960
That is why I hid the truth from you yesterday, My Lord.

91
00:05:24,080 --> 00:05:24,920
Mother.

92
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:27,480
Everything my mother said is true.

93
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,280
Father doesn't like us.

94
00:05:29,880 --> 00:05:30,920
And he doesn't like Mother.

95
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:33,440
My father did this.

96
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:41,560
What was that woman's name?

97
00:05:43,440 --> 00:05:44,040
Jin Yue.

98
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,600
We have news from the silver shop.

99
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,480
About four months ago,

100
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:58,000
Hu Pin had a longevity bracelet made at a silver shop in the Ghost Market.

101
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,640
The shop owner recognized the portrait.

102
00:06:00,200 --> 00:06:00,760
It's confirmed.

103
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,480
How much did it cost?

104
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:03,880
Ten guan.

105
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,120
Ten guan.

106
00:06:05,760 --> 00:06:07,240
That's three months' salary for a county magistrate.

107
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:09,280
Hu Pin is so poor.

108
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:10,680
Where did this money come from?

109
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:17,800
I think it came from here.

110
00:06:21,960 --> 00:06:22,440
What is this?

111
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,120
If I'm not mistaken...

112
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:26,800
A Wife-pawning Contract.

113
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,440
Let me try.

114
00:07:03,800 --> 00:07:04,720
Broker.

115
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,640
Hu Mei.

116
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,120
I'll go find this Hu Mei.

117
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:13,560
Hurry.

118
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:14,160
My Lord! My Lord!

119
00:07:14,840 --> 00:07:15,120
My Lord!

120
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,560
This is Hu Mei's home.

121
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:17,800
My Lord.

122
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,360
You should have said earlier that you're from the Dali Temple.

123
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:20,680
In that case,

124
00:07:21,080 --> 00:07:23,800
How could I have charged you so much money?

125
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,120
Thank you for the reward, My Lord.

126
00:07:27,520 --> 00:07:28,680
I'll take my leave now.

127
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:29,480
Mm-hmm.

128
00:07:31,960 --> 00:07:32,200
Let's go.

129
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:41,680
Who are you?

130
00:07:42,440 --> 00:07:43,440
What are you doing in my house?

131
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:47,640
Dali Temple questioning.

132
00:07:49,160 --> 00:07:50,120
I haven't done anything wrong.

133
00:07:50,520 --> 00:07:51,200
Why are you looking for me?

134
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,560
Do you know Tian Wan?

135
00:07:53,280 --> 00:07:53,720
I don't know him.

136
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:54,840
You answered so quickly.

137
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,560
Could his death be related to you?

138
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,320
M-My Lord.

139
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,120
You are wrongly accusing a common woman.

140
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,280
His death has nothing to do with me.

141
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,160
You can't accuse people falsely.

142
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,680
Whether it's false or not,

143
00:08:06,240 --> 00:08:06,960
a search will reveal.

144
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:07,960
Guiyi, search.

145
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,200
Everyone, come and look!

146
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,520
The officials are framing a good person!

147
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:13,000
You are bullying people with your power!

148
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:14,520
Everyone, come and look!

149
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,280
I will go to the Imperial City to sue you!

150
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,160
Drop this rascally act.

151
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:20,040
Look at this.

152
00:08:23,520 --> 00:08:24,880
The Tian Wan on this paper is dead.

153
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,480
If we can find you,

154
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:28,040
the killer can find you too.

155
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:30,080
You will be the next to die.

156
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:30,680
I...

157
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:31,960
If you want us to handle it,

158
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:32,720
then step aside.

159
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:34,000
If you don't want us to handle it,

160
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,160
we will leave right now.

161
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,160
Why not confess the truth?

162
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:45,880
My Lord.

163
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:47,240
It was Tian Wan.

164
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,200
He was anxious to have a son.

165
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:51,800
So I brokered a woman to be pawned to him.

166
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,160
That's all.

167
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:54,680
Who was the person pawned?

168
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:56,200
She seems to be called...

169
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:57,800
Jin Yue.

170
00:09:02,000 --> 00:09:03,640
Where is the pawned person from?

171
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:07,440
I have a poor relative.

172
00:09:07,760 --> 00:09:08,480
He needed money urgently.

173
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,600
So he asked me to find a taker.

174
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,880
Is it Hu Pin?

175
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:14,960
Yes.

176
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:19,720
My Lord.

177
00:09:23,160 --> 00:09:23,680
Found this.

178
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,160
Why are there two?

179
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:32,320
Both for the woman Jin Yue.

180
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,120
The wife-pawner is Liu Quan.

181
00:09:37,720 --> 00:09:39,000
That is Jin Yue's man.

182
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,880
That family is poor as dirt.

183
00:09:41,160 --> 00:09:42,120
And he is addicted to gambling.

184
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:43,640
Since Jin Yue married him,

185
00:09:43,840 --> 00:09:44,800
she hasn't given birth to a single child.

186
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:48,440
He heard a childless one could be pawned for a good price.

187
00:09:49,120 --> 00:09:49,760
In order to gamble,

188
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:51,640
he pawned his own wife.

189
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:52,960
My Lord.

190
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:54,600
I've said everything I know.

191
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,080
That killing has absolutely nothing to do with me.

192
00:09:59,560 --> 00:10:01,160
She was pawned by Liu Quan to Hu Pin.

193
00:10:01,560 --> 00:10:03,200
And then pawned by Hu Pin to Tian Wan.

194
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:04,640
The same woman,

195
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:06,120
was actually pawned twice by you people.

196
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,240
Treating her like an object to be traded at will.

197
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:09,280
You wicked people,

198
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,480
will surely suffer heaven's wrath.

199
00:10:11,640 --> 00:10:12,840
My Lord, I... I...

200
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,760
As a woman yourself,

201
00:10:18,120 --> 00:10:19,080
how could you be so cruel?

202
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:23,080
If your children were pawned to others,

203
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,200
how would you feel?

204
00:10:24,400 --> 00:10:24,840
My Lord.

205
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:27,760
I'm not the only one brokering wife-pawning.

206
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,560
So many people do it.

207
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,480
My Lord, spare my life.

208
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:37,600
Guiyi.

209
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:41,960
Guiyi.

210
00:10:42,920 --> 00:10:43,880
I can understand your feelings.

211
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,840
Now that Jin Yue is dead,

212
00:10:46,640 --> 00:10:47,640
she has left the filth of this world.

213
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:48,880
She has found peace.

214
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:49,560
Mm.

215
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,560
Let's go.

216
00:10:51,160 --> 00:10:52,520
Let's check Liu Quan's house.

217
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:53,240
Mm.
